The paper deals with the analysis of entropy rates and estimation entropy of a pair of correlated processes, with a focus on hidden Markov processes. This involves concepts from information theory, probability theory, and dynamical systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.ITP (Information Theory and Probability).
